### Pre-Wedding Video — Jharokha Arch Frame

The pre-wedding video sits at the very top of the Gallery section as the hero element, framed inside a Rajasthani Jharokha (palace window) arch.

**Frame Design: Jharokha Arch (Option A)**

- Shape: Pointed Rajasthani arch at top, straight gold borders on sides, flat bottom
- Border: 3px solid `#C9A96E` with inner shadow for carved depth effect
- Arch detail: SVG or CSS clip-path creating traditional pointed arch silhouette
- Corner ornaments: Small gold floral/leaf motifs at the two bottom corners where arch meets straight sides
- Inner padding: 8px between gold border and video (filled with `#111E36`)
- Outer glow: Subtle `#C9A96E` at 6% box-shadow (0 0 40px) — like lamplight on palace stone

**Video Player Specs**

| Property | Value | Aspect Ratio | 16:9 |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Width | 90% container (mobile), 70% container (desktop), max 640px | Thumbnail | First frame of video or custom poster with gold play button overlay |
| Play Button | 60px gold circle (#C9A96E), white ▶ icon centered, 50% opacity idle → 100% on hover/tap | Play Behavior | Inline playback (no modal). Tap play → video plays within the jharokha frame |
| Controls | Custom minimal: play/pause, progress bar (gold), mute toggle. No fullscreen, no download | Progress Bar | Thin 2px gold line below video inside frame |
| Autoplay | No. Poster image shown until guest taps play | Loading | Lazy — video loads only when Section 3 is entered |
| File Size Target | Under 8MB (compressed MP4, 720p) |  |  |

**Caption Below Frame**

- Text: "हमारी कहानी · Our Journey Together"
- Font: Cormorant Garamond 500 italic, 16px/18px
- Color: `#8A8578` (text-muted)
- Spacing: 16px below frame, 32px above photo divider

**Divider Between Video and Photos**

- Thin gold line (1px, `#C9A96E` at 25%) with a small centered marigold flower SVG motif (24px)
- 24px margin above and below divider

**Animation on Section Enter**

- Jharokha frame fades in first (0→1 opacity, 0.6s)
- Video thumbnail scales from 0.95→1.0 inside frame (0.4s, 0.2s delay)
- Caption fades in (0.3s, 0.5s delay)
- Photo grid loads after video frame is settled (0.8s delay)

