### Heartbeat Glow Effect

Subtle pulsing golden glow behind countdown -- like two hearts beating before the big day.

| Property | Value | Type | Radial gradient glow behind countdown boxes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Color | `#C9A96E` at 8-12% opacity | Pulse | Heartbeat: double-pulse (0.15s expand, 0.1s contract, 0.15s expand, 1.6s rest). 2s total cycle |
| Radius | 60% container expanding to 100% on pulse | Implementation | CSS box-shadow or radial-gradient on ::before pseudo |
| Reduced Motion | Static glow, no pulsing |  |  |

